K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-1: a'arya sarba ro ga pra sha ma ni n'a ma dh'a ra ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-3: 'phags pa nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa ces bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na; bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-7: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-9: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di zungs shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284a-13: gzhan dag la yang rgya cher yang dag par ston cig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-0: khrag @284b dang mkhris pa 'dres pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-8: yi dvags kyis zin pa'i gsang sngags kyi gzhi yin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-10: gang gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di dag las 'gal bar byed pa de ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-11: ngas lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten na ma mthong ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-14: gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di dag ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-17: sems can thams cad kyi mchog go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-19: chos thams cad kyi mchog go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-20: dge 'dun ni; tshogs thams cad kyi mchog go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-22: bden pa'i ngag 'dis bdag gis zos pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-25: myangs pa rnams legs par bde bar zhu bar gyur cig sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas dge slong de de dag yi rang ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-030:284b-27: 'phags pa nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
